      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BINNAWAY WIZARD (2) failed to come into contention last start after losing his position early at Murray Bridge, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at this track (20.02) beating OUR BELLA ROSE in a Grade 6 on April 13. Can make amends. ZING MATILDA (4) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 27 from 48 starts. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last five starts, the latest when third (22.83) at Murray Bridge. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Deserves a win and gets her chance. DIVERGENCE (5) was a strong winner (20.00) from box 1 last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths at this track. Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Can make it two on the bounce. ICE COOL BLUE (8) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.",
